---
import Button from '../parts/Button.astro';
---

<section
  class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-center pt-16"
  style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url('https://placehold.co/1920x1080/0891b2/white?text=Cebu+Island');"
>
  <div class="px-4 text-center text-white">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-6xl">
      セブ島を、自由に、安心して
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-200 md:text-xl">
      日本語ガイド付き・少人数制ローカルツアー。<br />
      ドローン空撮付き
    </p>
    <ul
      class="mx-auto mb-10 flex max-w-xl flex-col gap-3 text-left text-gray-100 md:flex-row md:justify-center md:gap-8 md:text-center"
    >
      <li class="flex items-center gap-2 md:flex-col">
        <span class="text-xl">🗣️</span>
        <span class="text-sm">日本語を話す現地ガイド</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-2 md:flex-col">
        <span class="text-xl">🇯🇵</span>
        <span class="text-sm">日本の会社が運営</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-2 md:flex-col">
        <span class="text-xl">🛡️</span>
        <span class="text-sm">許可証を持つツアー業者のみ</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <Button href="#footer-cta" size="lg">空き状況を確認する</Button>
  </div>
</section>
